---
// Componente Newsletter reutilizable
---

<article class="w-full">
    <div class="relative min-h-125 px-6! md:px-16! py-20! bg-[url(/boceto-contacto.jpg)] bg-cover bg-center flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center overflow-hidden rounded-sm shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)]">
        <!-- Overlay elegante -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-black/50 via-black/40 to-black/60 z-0"></div>
        
        <!-- Decoración superior -->
        <div class="relative z-10! mb-6!">
            <span class="block w-12! h-px! bg-[#B59410] mx-auto mb-4"></span>
            <span class="font-[Lato] text-xs uppercase tracking-[4px] text-white/70">Exclusivo</span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="relative z-10! font-[Bodoni_Moda] text-white! text-3xl! md:text-5xl! font-normal tracking-[3px] mb-6! drop-shadow-lg uppercase">
            Newsletter
        </h2>
        
        <p class="relative z-10! font-[Lato] text-white/90! font-bold! text-base! md:text-lg! tracking-wide mb-10! max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
            Sé el primero en descubrir nuevas obras, artistas emergentes y eventos exclusivos de la galería.
        </p>

        <form class="relative z-10! w-full max-w-lg">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mb-6!">
                <input 
                    type="email" 
                    placeholder="Tu correo electrónico" 
                    class="w-full px-6! py-4! bg-white/95 border-0 rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#B59410] font-[Lato] text-[#1A1A1A] text-sm tracking-wide placeholder:text-[#8C8C8C] placeholder:uppercase placeholder:text-xs placeholder:tracking-[2px] transition-all duration-300"
                    required
                />
                <button 
                    type="submit" 
                    class="w-full bg-[#8B0000] hover:bg-[#B59410] text-white font-[Lato] font-normal text-sm px-8! py-4! rounded-sm transition-all duration-300 ease-out hover:shadow-[0_8px_25px_rgba(181,148,16,0.3)] uppercase tracking-[3px]"
                >
                    Suscribirse
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3! text-left">
                <input 
                    type="checkbox" 
                    id="terminos" 
                    name="terminos" 
                    class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 accent-[#B59410] cursor-pointer shrink-0 rounded-sm"
                    required
                />
                <label 
                    for="terminos" 
                    class="font-[Lato] text-xs! text-white/70! font-light! leading-relaxed cursor-pointer hover:text-white/90 transition-colors duration-300"
                >
                    Acepto la política de privacidad y el tratamiento de mis datos personales.
                </label>
            </div>
        </form>

        <!-- Decoración inferior -->
        <div class="relative z-10! mt-10!">
            <span class="block w-12! h-px! bg-[#B59410] mx-auto"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
</article>
